{"tid":344903,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"同女朋友一齊4年幾","createTime":"2017-08-02T15:12:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-03T11:35:50.000Z","uid":16079,"like":62,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f2ea2c8581cf8a15a2df5ba67b93bcbb716127ee","tid":344903,"uid":16079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T15:12:33.000Z","msg":"今日分左手<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最近佢返工開始愈來愈少覆我whatsapp<br />\n佢話休息會想睇書或者合埋眼而唔想覆電話<br />\n我明佢忙<br />\n咁我問佢食飯唔覆得？<br />\n佢話想同同事傾多啲計<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今日終於頂唔順<br />\n同佢講分手<br />\n其實我都feel到佢最近當我朋友咁多過男朋友<br />\n我只係呃自己話所有野都仲有得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上年分過手<br />\n佢提出嘅<br />\n話有自己目標<br />\n我做死狗求佢一齊返佢唔肯<br />\n最後佢一個月後搵返我<br />\n我原諒佢<br />\n但自此冇晒信心<br />\n以前一齊講咩promise 咩永遠原來係假<br />\n心入面一直有條刺<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歡迎來護眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ec9df9c84129934f5d2b4ef91a5fe174d88de7d","tid":344903,"uid":16079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T15:12:59.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2549f7fc1eacd4357253ae795882d6c73e710901","tid":344903,"uid":16079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T15:13:33.000Z","msg":"其實我一直唔講係咪可以當冇事發生過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84382c7250ddee1f3ec33591fc0f8cae8f2c1790","tid":344903,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T15:13:45.000Z","msg":"咩年紀<br />\n使唔使咁灰"},{"pid":"856203150ea07e2a29ce7c8110ef7fa6eb5e1e83","tid":344903,"uid":71728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T15:14:01.000Z","msg":"屌過未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"478b98711ec2481c82de1f5b73c4