n前幾日出街佢都好似想避開我 果刻想問佢做咩<br />\n始終有陰影<br />\n事關上年佢又係好冷漠<br />\n提出分手都係whatsapp 講句就走左<br />\n搵佢解釋冇覆 點都唔覆<br />\n最後自己搵返我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我今次whatsapp分手都唔係好過份姐"},{"pid":"672b3b599f22171b0490879a9dc08326809ee8e2","tid":344903,"uid":16079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T17:35:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一齊幾耐都係假 但偏偏自己又做唔到鐵石心腸<br />\n放過自己啦巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得要面對始終都要<br />\n講出來都預左會有壞結果<br />\n但都好過呃住自己<br />\n唔開心係有<br />\n我都希望只會呢幾日唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9985aa0ea23e878d00106b787e3412020d47f4d1","tid":344903,"uid":16079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T17:36:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去下旅行多d同唔同人接觸/增值自己 就會發現世界好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過呢一刻個心喇下喇下就梗㗎啦</blockquote><br />\n遲下想自己一個去<br />\n有冇教學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nbudget/咩國家/幾時</blockquote><br />\n$5000/未去過的亞洲地方/9月頭"},{"pid":"690232af93a03ef3ded080dcc7c01558b0707a02","tid":344903,"uid":16079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T17:37:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都啱啱分左 三年幾可以忘記得一乾二淨 而我就成日諗起佢</blockquote><br />\n女人真係好絕<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fe149558396d836132019e39fb9111d42d9396e","tid":344903,"uid":126437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T17:58:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都啱啱分左 三年幾可以忘記得一乾二淨 而我就成日諗起佢</blockquote><br />\n女人真係好絕<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n前幾個月U畢業前分手，喺Grad Ceremony 嗰陣時見到佢好尷尬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5f60393ad146bf5e7ff0083a173b78896770fde","tid":344903,"uid":61264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply